{"tid":2430064,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"電器公司向員工提供 3700 個住宿單位 90 後做到退休可直接擁有","createTime":"2021-03-02T16:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T08:36:45.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2cdb719a96a8cd3b4ad05015e505db1886d6f3fa","tid":2430064,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2890000/2890561/lou2_groupphoto_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2890000%2F2890561%2Flou2_groupphoto_600.jpg&h=645994eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n内媒報道，格力電器董事長董明珠接受訪問時提及公司有一項專門吸收年輕人才的政策。她指出公司在未來 2 年會為員工提供房屋，預計能提供 3,700 間套房供新入職員工入住，以達至新入職科技人員「一人一套房」。她豪言：「只要大學生來了，就是一套房」而員工只要做到退休，該套房亦歸他所有。<br />\n<br />\n她認爲，「送樓」措施可吸引年輕專才為公司長期服務，為格力電器帶來「格局」上的變化。而其他員工則可花更多精力、時間在工作上。據指，這 3,700 間套房將命名為「格力明珠廣場」，將座落珠海市香洲區，當中包括 11 棟住宅大廈、1 棟商業配套大樓及 1 間幼兒園，總投資金額為 20 億元人民幣（約 HK $24 億）。而住宅單位基本有 2 房 1 廳，面積各有不同。"},{"pid":"2d547b9923cdfaeeca8be1561025bf52301aa295","tid":2430064,"uid":7223,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"臨退休炒左佢咪白做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8990a1e5cfb848fe5f5f19c418656b6494a38f","tid":2430064,"uid":28913,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2d547b9923cdfaeeca8be1561025bf52301aa295","tid":2430064,"uid":7223,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"臨退休炒左佢咪白做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"好出奇? <br />\n之前支那華為就係想換血炒鳩